  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Chalet Noella is one of our three Inghams chalets in Val Thorens, sharing an exclusive building. Each chalet is independently hosted and Chalet Noella has four bedrooms. The nearest piste is just 100 metres away and there's a shared sauna and steam room to enjoy at the end of the day. Offered on a chalet catering board basis, you'll enjoy breakfast, afternoon tea and cakes, dinner and wine included with your stay. This chalet sleeps 8 people and can be booked for sole occupancy.</p>
<p><strong>Save £100pp when you pre-book your ski pass and lift hire/carriage.</strong></p>]]></listingDescription>
